items.title: When Facebook Outs Your Most Personal Secrets
items.description: "I remember I was miserable and said, Facebook decided to tell my dad that I was gay."

items.title: Woman Sues Apple Over Use Of Her Eye Photo
items.description: A Swiss photographer is alleging Apple never properly licensed a photo used in ads for the Retina-display Macbook Pros.
items.y:title: Woman Sues Apple Over Use Of Her Eye Photo

items.title: Microsoft Investigating Halo 4 Leak
items.description: We don't know yet if the full campaign of Halo 4 has leaked to the Internet.
items.y:title: Microsoft Investigating Halo 4 Leak

items.title: Prepare To Pay For Your Privacy
items.description: As surveillance technology gets cheaper much faster than the world’s poorest get wealthier, it may not be long before privacy — any privacy — will begin to feel, seem, and even cost like a luxury.
items.y:title: Prepare To Pay For Your Privacy

items.title: Britain Has Weapons To Fight A War With Aliens, Says Former Government Adviser
items.description: Nick Pope, who worked for the Ministry of Defence for 21 years, said that while Britain doesn't have a war plan, it certainly had sophisticated enough weaponry to defend itself.
items.y:title: Britain Has Weapons To Fight A War With Aliens, Says Former Government Adviser

items.title: Neanderthals... They're Just Like Us?
items.description: Well, not exactly. But new discoveries have had a surprisingly humanizing effect.
items.y:title: Neanderthals... They're Just Like Us?

items.title: Scientists Uncover Mystery Of Ball Lightning
items.description: A team of Australian scientists believe they have uncovered the cause of one of nature's most bizarre phenomenon - ball lightning.
items.y:title: Scientists Uncover Mystery Of Ball Lightning

items.title: Really? Study Says PMS Moodiness Is Just A Myth
items.description: Not that reluctant attitudes about menstrual mood swings were ever a legitimate excuse to exclude women from activities, but now New Zealand researchers have formally debunked the mythology surrounding PMS.
items.y:title: Really? Study Says PMS Moodiness Is Just A Myth

items.title: Why Do We Hate Mondays?
items.description: Despite the beating that Mondays have taken in pop songs — Fats Domino crooned “Blue Monday, how I hate blue Monday” — the day does not deserve its gloomy reputation.
items.y:title: Why Do We Hate Mondays?

items.title: Inside Osama Bin Laden's Final Hours
items.description: How did the raid that killed bin Laden get green-lighted? In an adaptation from his new book, Mark Bowden weaves together accounts from Obama and top decision-makers for the full story behind the daring operation.
items.y:title: Inside Osama Bin Laden's Final Hours
